				<td colspan="2"><span>As everyone else said, yes bards can tank... with AGI Maxed at 280 (don't have plannar yet) and LR3 (working my way to LR5) mobs miss 80% of the blows (counting parry and dodge), so yes, with 1200+ AC (preferable 1400 AC or so) bards can tank no problem.
<br />

<br />
The problem is holding agro... never happens... and BoC is SOOO expensive to buy... funy guilds don't give BoCs to bards but then they put them up for sale in Bazaar.
<br />

<br />
Sure, with TDoK and chaining 4 Dots I have held agro over rogues and nukers, but then I am not helping group as I would if I twist hastes, ds, etc... I did tank cause MA LDed on a LDoN. 
<br />

