				<td colspan="2"><span>Well, there is a BIG difference between CAN tank and SHOULD tank.  I CAN tank in LDON even on hard, for a short time.  But I am costing the healers a LOT more mana than when our warrior tanks.  So on hard, my first priority is to mez adds, not off-tank them like I do on normal level.  I could only hold agro at this level if I completely changed out songs and went full-offensive which is not what my group needs.  Bottom line, I should not even be trying to tank, though I can in a pinch.  We've had our warrior go LD during fights in hard LDON and we've always survived with me tanking till she got back.  But it isn't preferable.
