				<td colspan="2"><span>To tank upper levels, gear and AA is a necessity.  If you don't have weapons that hold aggro, it's not worth tanking unless it's a necessity because the songs you use to keep aggro are underpowered relative to how well you can buff your group with utility. I've personally always wanted to be a tank-worthy bard... the reality is, in a grouping situation, it's oftentimes frustrating because it's harder to keep up the full lineup of songs with stuns / interrupts.  So, if you can handle it, it's fun sometimes for a change, but we're not meant to do it fulltime ;)</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
