				<td colspan="2"><span>Depends on the context.  An elemental equiped bard should be able to tank quite a few luclin level mobs, some more painful than others.
<br />

<br />
It really depends on the time and energy one has put into their toon.  A fully bazaar/ldon equiped bard should have decent hp/ac for regular exp groups.
<br />

<br />
There are times when I have to ask pickup/random tanks to quit taunting because they're getting mauled and slowing us down :\  So yeah, at times I'd prefer to be tanking if the other isn't suitable.
<br />

<br />
To hold agro typically 1 chant is enough for most non-taunting classes.  For rogues make that 2 chants and you're good to go.</span></td>
